column4: "Lots of opportunities for Whole Tone Scales in this wonderful song - can be played with the first 2 bars of the A section  as Eb9#11 then Db9#11 - 2 dominant chords that contain all the 6  notes of the Whole Tone scale beginning on any of these Db Eb F G\012"
"See The New Real Book (Volume 1) page 51 for lead sheet.\012"
